file.name: positive2.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Simple API Overview
  version: 1.0.0
  contact:
    name: contact
    url: https://www.google.com/
    email: user@gmail.c
paths: {}
components:
  schemas:
    ErrorModel:
      type: object
      required:
        - message
        - code
      properties:
        message:
          type: string
        code:
          type: integer
          minimum: 100
          maximum: 600
      allOf:
        - "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorModel"
        - type: object
          required:
            - code
          properties:
            code:
              type: integer
              minimum: 100
              maximum: 600
      additionalProperties:
        - type: object
          required:
            - code
          properties:
            code:
              type: string
